:name:
Storytelling

:pool: 
Reason

:p: 
R

:coretxt:
Stories contain small pieces of truth.
Storytelling is about knowing stories and being able to recite those.
Skilled storytellers know what things stories try to teach and are able to use that specific knowledge.
Storytelling is when trying to find what is true about something that could be found in stories.

